sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente HTTP
    participant TXI as TenantInterceptor
    participant TXS as TenantDataSourceService
    participant NU as NegocioUnificadoRepository
    participant TXDS as TenantRoutingDataSource
    participant Controller as Tenant Controller
    participant DB as MySQL (Tenant DB)

    Client->>TXI: GET /api/tenant/... (X-TENANT-ID: tenant-123)
    TXI->>TXI: Extraer X-TENANT-ID del header
    TXI->>TXS: ensureTenantDataSource(tenant-123)
    TXS->>TXS: Limpiar TenantContext (evitar ruteo circular)
    TXS->>NU: findByTenantId(tenant-123)
    NU-->>TXS: NegocioUnificado (ip, puerto, db, usuario)
    TXS->>TXS: createDataSource(negocio)
    TXS->>TXS: Crear HikariDataSource (pool 30 conexiones)
    TXS->>TXDS: addTenantDataSource(tenant-123, ds)
    TXS-->>TXI: OK
    TXI->>TXI: TenantContext.setCurrentTenant(tenant-123)
    TXI->>TXI: Continuar con handler del controlador
    Controller->>TXDS: determineCurrentLookupKey()
    TXDS-->>Controller: tenant-123
    Controller->>DB: Consulta BD del tenant
    DB-->>Controller: Resultados
    Controller-->>Client: HTTP 200 Response
